00:03:08.734 --> 00:03:14.554
Long story short, there was strong opposition to the new king’s relationship with

00:03:14.554 --> 00:03:21.914
this American divorcée, and instead of leaving her, he left the monarchy, abdicating

00:03:22.034 --> 00:03:27.724
his position as king and passing the throne to his brother, Elizabeth’s father.

00:03:28.614 --> 00:03:32.014
To state the obvious, this was unexpected.

00:03:32.334 --> 00:03:34.304
